~~~~Main control interface tasks~~~~

Name: Frame and menu
Descr: set up a frame and a menu with the names of the games as items
Time: 1 hour

Name: Link menu to games
Descr: set up functions to launch games when corresponding menu items are clicked
Time: 1 hour


